    /* the following line of text shows Old School Runescape market place (oldschool forums) ,you can change display:block; to  visibility:hidden; and that will hide it if you want. if you have titles on feel free to change the top -484px top: -440px;  so that the title isnt ontop of oldschool advice
    
    
    */
